::System Requirements::


OS: Windows 7 - Windows XP not supported 
Processor: Intel Core2 Duo E8200 2.66 GHz or AMD Phenom X3 8750 2.4 GHz 
Memory: 2 GB RAM 
Graphics: Nvidia GeForce 8800GT 512 MB or ATI Radeon HD 3870 512 MB 
DirectX: Version 9.0c 
Hard Drive: 3 GB available space 
Additional Notes: Broadband connection required for multiplayer gameplay


::Greetz and Respect::


ALL CREDIT Goes to REVOLT for Ripping and a Special friend for Distribution.


::Uploader Notes::


This game is online only, and there are 2 ways you can join the Gameplay, One is

Host and second is Client and its instructions are available in the Information 

given above so we wish all of you would like this online shooter game with modern

graphics and we see our old friend group REVOLT rise from the grave, Cheers :)


